{"_id": "16f53472844251a7", "name": "Problem Solver", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "", "benefit": "As a Swift Action once per turn, you can designate a single Vehicle within your line of sight whose Pilot can hear and understand you. That Pilot's Vehicle ignores Difficult Terrain until the start of your next turn, and the Pilot gains a +5 insight bonus on all Pilot checks made to avoid Hazards and Collisions until the start of your next turn.", "description": {"value": "As a Swift Action once per turn, you can designate a single Vehicle within your line of sight whose Pilot can hear and understand you. That Pilot's Vehicle ignores Difficult Terrain until the start of your next turn, and the Pilot gains a +5 insight bonus on all Pilot checks made to avoid Hazards and Collisions until the start of your next turn."}, "class": "b85240cf77cf95eb", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Military Engineer", "treeId": "e32009b1b0aee8c9", "tags": ["controller", "evasion", "striker"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 0, "type": "untyped", "predicates": [], "enabled": false, "priority": 500, "description": "[REQUIRES MANUAL MAPPING] Problem Solver"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.problem_solver", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.404Z", "detectedPredicates": []}}}
{"_id": "1718ec6cdf765a57", "name": "Greater Penetrating Attack", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "Greater Weapon Focus (Chosen Weapon), Penetrating Attack (Chosen Weapon)", "benefit": "Choose a single Exotic Weapon or weapon group with which you're proficient. Whenever you make a successful attack against a target using the chosen Exotic Weapon or weapon from the chosen group, you treat your target's Damage Reduction as if it were 10 points lower when determining the results of your attack.", "description": {"value": "Choose a single Exotic Weapon or weapon group with which you're proficient. Whenever you make a successful attack against a target using the chosen Exotic Weapon or weapon from the chosen group, you treat your target's Damage Reduction as if it were 10 points lower when determining the results of your attack.\n\nThis replaces the effects of the Penetrating Attack Talent."}, "class": "c4dbedcf989cb6b2", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Elite Trooper", "treeId": "2f720d8b061f9bd0", "tags": ["damage-reduction", "feat-chain", "soldier", "talent-chain"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 0, "type": "untyped", "predicates": [], "enabled": false, "priority": 500, "description": "[REQUIRES MANUAL MAPPING] Greater Penetrating Attack"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.greater_penetrating_attack", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.404Z", "detectedPredicates": []}}}
{"_id": "17518b7669101122", "name": "Combined Fire", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "Charisma 13", "benefit": "As a Swift Action, you may designate a single creature, Vehicle or object within your line of sight as the target of . Any Weapon Batteries attacking the target deal an extra die of damage for every 2 points by which their attack roll exceeds the target's Reflex Defense (instead of every 3 points). In addition, when using the Tactical Fire option for a Capital Ship, you may designated a weapon or Weapon Battery to make a single attack. As a Full-Round Action, you can designate a number of Vehicles equal to your Officer Class Level and within your line of sight. Those Vehicles may immediately move a number of squares equal to their speed.", "description": "As a Swift Action, you may designate a single creature, Vehicle or object within your line of sight as the target of . Any Weapon Batteries attacking the target deal an extra die of damage for every 2 points by which their attack roll exceeds the target's Reflex Defense (instead of every 3 points). In addition, when using the Tactical Fire option for a Capital Ship, you may designated a weapon or Weapon Battery to make a single attack. As a Full-Round Action, you can designate a number of Vehicles equal to your Officer Class Level and within your line of sight. Those Vehicles may immediately move a number of squares equal to their speed.", "class": "f62ca2e639cab614", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Soldier", "treeId": "057a978a7dc1d5a7", "tags": ["action-economy", "controller", "defender", "feat-chain", "mobility", "positioning", "soldier", "striker", "sustained-damage", "talent-chain"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "MODIFIER", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "damage", "type": "untyped", "value": 2, "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Migrated from AE system.damage"}]}}, "effects": [{"_id": "6f88b513-9d62-4971-a686-72668a6da31d", "name": "Combined Fire", "icon": "icons/svg/gun.svg", "changes": [{"key": "system.damage", "mode": 2, "value": "2"}], "disabled": true, "duration": {}, "flags": {"swse": {"source": "talent", "talentName": "Combined Fire", "migratedToPassive": true}}}], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.combined_fire"}}}
{"_id": "175c46931a9e474a", "name": "Observant", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "Trained in Persuasion", "description": "Any Talent from the Influence Talent Tree, Inspiration Talent Tree, or Leadership Talent Tree You are programmed to oversee other Droids. You can use each of the following actions once per encounter: Combat Support: As a Standard Action, you automatically Aid Another on an allied Droid's attack roll, provided you are capable of using the Aid Another action to assist that ally. If you also have Weapon Focus Feat, you increase the bonus provided by the Aid Another action from +2 to +3. Director: As a Standard Action, you automatically Aid Another Droid with a Skill you are Trained in. If you also have Skill Focus in that Skill, you increase the Aid Another bonus from +2 to +5. Instant Action: As a Swift Action, you grant one ally a Swift Action that it can use immediately as a Free Action. Reference Book: Star Wars Saga Edition Scavenger's Guide to Droids You know how to subtly massage translations. When one of your allies is attempting to use the Persuasion skill to change the Attitude of a creature that does not understand your ally, you add +2 to the ally's Persuasion check results if you perform the translation.", "benefit": "Any Talent from the Influence Talent Tree, Inspiration Talent Tree, or Leadership Talent Tree You are programmed to oversee other Droids. You can use each of the following actions once per encounter: Combat Support: As a Standard Action, you automatically Aid Another on an allied Droid's attack roll, provided you are capable of using the Aid Another action to assist that ally. If you also have Weapon Focus Feat, you increase the bonus provided by the Aid Another action from +2 to +3. Director: As a Standard Action, you automatically Aid Another Droid with a Skill you are Trained in. If you also have Skill Focus in that Skill, you increase the Aid Another bonus from +2 to +5. Instant Action: As a Swift Action, you grant one ally a Swift Action that it can use immediately as a Free Action. Reference Book: Star Wars Saga Edition Scavenger's Guide to Droids You know how to subtly massage translations. When one of your allies is attempting to use the Persuasion skill to change the Attitude of a creature that does not understand your ally, you add +2 to the ally's Persuasion check results if you perform the translation.", "class": "", "category": "", "costNumeric": null, "treeId": "af077700c1b8433f", "tags": ["action_economy", "awareness", "droid", "feat_chain", "leader", "leadership", "mobility", "new_action", "perception", "persuasion", "skills", "social", "standard_action", "striker", "support", "swift_action", "talent_chain", "uncategorized_talent"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "skill", "value": 2, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["turn.once-per-round"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Observant"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.404Z", "detectedPredicates": ["turn.once-per-round"]}}}
