{"_id": "45c4e72d74c44acb", "name": "Mystical Link", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "", "description": {"value": "The Force guides you in unexpected ways. As a Standard Action, make a DC 30 Use the Force check. If the check is successful, you gain one of the following benefits, as selected by the Gamemaster:"}, "benefit": "The Force guides you in unexpected ways. As a Standard Action, make a DC 30 Use the Force check. If the check is successful, you gain one of the following benefits, as selected by the Gamemaster:", "class": "", "category": "", "costNumeric": null, "treeId": "e35ee41362604227", "tags": ["action_economy", "balance", "damage_reduction", "force", "force_execution", "new_action", "standard_action", "support", "survivability", "tree_e35ee41362604227", "uncategorized_talent", "use_the_force", "will_defense"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "defense.will", "value": 2, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["turn.once-per-round"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Mystical Link"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.411Z", "detectedPredicates": ["turn.once-per-round"]}}}
{"_id": "45d8f7a583314692", "name": "Draw a Bead", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "Precision Shot, Base Attack Bonus +10", "description": {"value": "Once per round, you can spend a single Swift Action to designate a single enemy who is not within Point-Blank Range. When you make a successful ranged attack roll that deals damage against the designated enemy, add your Dexterity bonus (minimum +1) to the damage roll.\n\nThis effect lasts until the target is unconscious, dead, or leaves your line of sight. You can have only one enemy designated in this manner."}, "benefit": "Once per round, you can spend a single Swift Action to designate a single enemy who is not within Point-Blank Range. When you make a successful ranged attack roll that deals damage against the designated enemy, add your Dexterity bonus (minimum +1) to the damage roll.", "class": "", "category": "", "costNumeric": null, "treeId": "d203a51d6d0a4c65", "tags": ["action_economy", "controller", "defender", "offense_ranged", "positioning", "precision_damage", "ranged", "sniping", "swift_action", "targeting", "tree_d203a51d6d0a4c65", "uncategorized_talent"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "defense.reflex", "value": 2, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["defense.reflex", "attack.with-ranged", "turn.once-per-round"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Draw a Bead"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.411Z", "detectedPredicates": ["defense.reflex", "attack.with-ranged", "turn.once-per-round"]}}}
{"_id": "4632b4bf79044752", "name": "Nature Sense", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "", "description": "Prerequisites: Trained in Perception, You ignore Concealment (including Total Concealment) from darkness. However, you cannot perceive colors in total darkness. Additionally, at close range (within 10 squares), you ignore Concealment and Cover for purposes of Perception checks, and take no penalty from poor visibility while Tracking. Homebrew Reference Book: Saga Edition All-Purpose Sourcebook As a Swift Action, you may use The Force to calm Hostile and Unfriendly Beasts. Make a Persuasion check; if the result equals or exceeds the targets' Will Defense, its Attitude immediately shifts to Indifferent. You can affect a number of creatures whose total combined levels do not exceed your Character Level. This is a Mind-Affecting effect. Homebrew Reference Book: Saga Edition All-Purpose Sourcebook You gain the ability to comprehend any spoken language. This does not grant you the ability to speak an unfamiliar language, only to understand them through The Force. Homebrew Reference Book: Saga Edition All-Purpose Sourcebook", "benefit": "Prerequisites: Trained in Perception, You ignore Concealment (including Total Concealment) from darkness. However, you cannot perceive colors in total darkness. Additionally, at close range (within 10 squares), you ignore Concealment and Cover for purposes of Perception checks, and take no penalty from poor visibility while Tracking. Homebrew Reference Book: Saga Edition All-Purpose Sourcebook As a Swift Action, you may use The Force to calm Hostile and Unfriendly Beasts. Make a Persuasion check; if the result equals or exceeds the targets' Will Defense, its Attitude immediately shifts to Indifferent. You can affect a number of creatures whose total combined levels do not exceed your Character Level. This is a Mind-Affecting effect. Homebrew Reference Book: Saga Edition All-Purpose Sourcebook You gain the ability to comprehend any spoken language. This does not grant you the ability to speak an unfamiliar language, only to understand them through The Force. Homebrew Reference Book: Saga Edition All-Purpose Sourcebook", "class": "", "category": "", "costNumeric": null, "treeId": "ed899f9f41fc1391", "tags": ["action_economy", "beast_companion", "cover", "dark_side", "defender", "defense", "force", "force_defense", "force_execution", "leader", "mobility", "nature", "perception", "persuasion", "positioning", "skills", "social", "stealth", "support", "survival", "swift_action", "tree_ed899f9f41fc1391", "uncategorized_talent", "use_the_force"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "defense.will", "value": 2, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["defense.will"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Nature Sense"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.411Z", "detectedPredicates": ["defense.will"]}}}
{"_id": "4635850263c7bf94", "name": "Misplaced Loyalty", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "Dirty Tactics", "benefit": "As a Swift Action once per turn, you can make a Persuasion check against the Will Defense of all opponents within your line of sight. If successful, a target cannot attack you if one of your allies is within 6 squares of you.", "description": {"value": "As a Swift Action once per turn, you can make a Persuasion check against the Will Defense of all opponents within your line of sight. If successful, a target cannot attack you if one of your allies is within 6 squares of you.\n\nYou may not gain the benefit of this Talent if another character within 6 squares of you has used this talent since the end of your last turn. You may not use this Talent in the same round as the Soldier's Draw Fire Talent."}, "class": "8c58016e587dd2c7", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Noble", "prerequisitesStructured": {"type": "all", "conditions": [{"type": "talent", "id": "swse.talent.dirty_tactics"}], "_source": "canonical-csv"}, "treeId": "e91cc675fbf9ba6e", "tags": ["defender", "feat-chain", "noble", "positioning", "skills", "social", "support", "talent-chain"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "defense.will", "value": 2, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["defense.will"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Misplaced Loyalty"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.misplaced_loyalty", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.411Z", "detectedPredicates": ["defense.will"]}}}
{"_id": "463ae052e705eaf3", "name": "Wrong Decision", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "", "benefit": "Each time you are attacked, the opponent that attacked you takes a -2 morale penalty to its Will Defense until the end of your next turn. This penalty is not cumulative, so if a target makes multiple attacks against you it only incurs the penalty once per turn.", "description": {"value": "Each time you are attacked, the opponent that attacked you takes a -2 morale penalty to its Will Defense until the end of your next turn. This penalty is not cumulative, so if a target makes multiple attacks against you it only incurs the penalty once per turn."}, "class": "fc815ae3ca4bf726", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Corporate Agent", "treeId": "45c4007d09c01839", "tags": ["category_corporate_agent", "control", "deception", "defender", "leader", "persuasion", "social"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "defense.will", "value": 2, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["defense.will"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Wrong Decision"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.wrong_decision", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.411Z", "detectedPredicates": ["defense.will"]}}}
