{"_id": "8eace9d86fc60711", "name": "Lifesaver", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "Bodyguard's Sacrifice", "benefit": "Once per encounter as a Reaction, when an ally takes damage that equals or exceeds its Damage Threshold or reduces it to 0 Hit Points, you can move up to your speed provided you end your movement adjacent to that ally. This movement provokes Attacks of Opportunity as normal, you take all of the damage that triggered this Talent's use, and your ally takes no damage.", "description": {"value": "Once per encounter as a Reaction, when an ally takes damage that equals or exceeds its Damage Threshold or reduces it to 0 Hit Points, you can move up to your speed provided you end your movement adjacent to that ally. This movement provokes Attacks of Opportunity as normal, you take all of the damage that triggered this Talent's use, and your ally takes no damage."}, "class": "c4dbedcf989cb6b2", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Elite Trooper", "prerequisitesStructured": {"type": "all", "conditions": [{"type": "talent", "id": "swse.talent.bodyguards_sacrifice"}], "_source": "canonical-csv"}, "treeId": "c92c2cbc79b8a515", "tags": ["controller", "damage-reduction", "feat-chain", "mobility", "positioning", "soldier", "striker", "support", "talent-chain"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 2, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["proximity.ally-nearby", "turn.once-per-round"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Lifesaver"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.lifesaver", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.421Z", "detectedPredicates": ["proximity.ally-nearby", "turn.once-per-round"]}}}
{"_id": "8ed7b1889b1416d4", "name": "Terrify", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "Frighten, Inspire Fear I, Inspire Fear II", "benefit": "As a Standard Action, you can make a Persuasion check against a target that is within your line of sight and that is also affected by your Inspire Fear Talent. If you equal or exceed the target's Will Defense, then on its next turn the target must spend at least one Move Action to move away from you. If the target is somehow prevented from doing so, then the penalty from the Inspire Fear Talent doubles until the start of your next turn. This is a Mind-Affecting Fear effect.", "description": {"value": "As a Standard Action, you can make a Persuasion check against a target that is within your line of sight and that is also affected by your Inspire Fear Talent. If you equal or exceed the target's Will Defense, then on its next turn the target must spend at least one Move Action to move away from you. If the target is somehow prevented from doing so, then the penalty from the Inspire Fear Talent doubles until the start of your next turn. This is a Mind-Affecting Fear effect."}, "class": "324631ca844a88be", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Crime Lord", "prerequisitesStructured": {"type": "all", "conditions": [{"type": "talent", "id": "swse.talent.inspire_fear_ii"}, {"type": "talent", "id": "swse.talent.frighten"}], "_source": "canonical-csv"}, "treeId": "c1be604242cb328f", "tags": ["controller", "feat-chain", "force", "force-control", "mobility", "skills", "social", "talent-chain"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 0, "type": "untyped", "predicates": [], "enabled": false, "priority": 500, "description": "[REQUIRES MANUAL MAPPING] Terrify"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.terrify", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.421Z", "detectedPredicates": []}}}
{"_id": "8f388280e0d1b244", "name": "Hasty Withdrawal", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "", "benefit": "As a Swift Action once per turn, you target a number of allies equal to your Charisma bonus (minimum 1). Each targeted ally must be within 12 squares of you and in your line of sight. Each ally you target can take the Withdraw Action immediately as a Free Action. The normal rules for Withdrawing otherwise apply.", "description": {"value": "As a Swift Action once per turn, you target a number of allies equal to your Charisma bonus (minimum 1). Each targeted ally must be within 12 squares of you and in your line of sight. Each ally you target can take the Withdraw Action immediately as a Free Action. The normal rules for Withdrawing otherwise apply."}, "class": "30b9cd24b80ebf46", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Officer", "treeId": "61b74c82cb56876c", "tags": ["action-economy", "mobility", "precision", "skills", "stealth", "support"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 0, "type": "untyped", "predicates": [], "enabled": false, "priority": 500, "description": "[REQUIRES MANUAL MAPPING] Hasty Withdrawal"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.hasty_withdrawal", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.421Z", "detectedPredicates": []}}}
{"_id": "8f64ec5c81784b2d", "name": "Tyia Adept", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "", "description": "When an ally within 12 squares of you and in your line of sight takes damage or moves down the Condition Track by any means, you can designate a different ally within 12 squares of you and in your line of sight as a Reaction. The ally you designate gain Bonus Hit Points equal to 5 + your Charisma modifier (minimum +1). Damage is subtracted from Bonus Hit Points first, and any Bonus Hit Points remaining at the end of the encounter are lost. Prerequisite: You can designate an ally within 12 squares of you and in your line of sight once per turn as a Swift Action; that ally immediately takes its Second Wind if it has not yet done so in this encounter. Whenever you are targeted by a Force Power with the [Dark Side] descriptor, you can spend a Force Point as a Reaction to give the creature that used that Force Power against you a penalty on its Use the Force check to activate the power equal to its Dark Side Score. You can choose to have any Force Power you activate deal Stun Damage instead of normal damage. As a Swift Action, you can spend a Force Point to designate one non-Droid ally within 12 squares of you and in your line of sight. Until the end of your next turn, whenever you or the targeted ally takes damage from any source, you take half of the damage and your ally takes half of the damage. This halving of damage takes place before the damage is compared to your respective Damage Thresholds.", "benefit": "When an ally within 12 squares of you and in your line of sight takes damage or moves down the Condition Track by any means, you can designate a different ally within 12 squares of you and in your line of sight as a Reaction. The ally you designate gain Bonus Hit Points equal to 5 + your Charisma modifier (minimum +1). Damage is subtracted from Bonus Hit Points first, and any Bonus Hit Points remaining at the end of the encounter are lost. Prerequisite: You can designate an ally within 12 squares of you and in your line of sight once per turn as a Swift Action; that ally immediately takes its Second Wind if it has not yet done so in this encounter. Whenever you are targeted by a Force Power with the [Dark Side] descriptor, you can spend a Force Point as a Reaction to give the creature that used that Force Power against you a penalty on its Use the Force check to activate the power equal to its Dark Side Score. You can choose to have any Force Power you activate deal Stun Damage instead of normal damage. As a Swift Action, you can spend a Force Point to designate one non-Droid ally within 12 squares of you and in your line of sight. Until the end of your next turn, whenever you or the targeted ally takes damage from any source, you take half of the damage and your ally takes half of the damage. This halving of damage takes place before the damage is compared to your respective Damage Thresholds.", "class": "", "category": "", "costNumeric": null, "treeId": "9a5efe5d0e9b43a1", "tags": ["action_economy", "condition_removal", "controller", "dark_side", "defender", "defense", "droid", "force", "force_capacity", "force_control", "force_execution", "force_offense", "force_point_spend", "force_power_synergy", "meditation", "mobility", "positioning", "reaction", "resource_spend", "striker", "support", "swift_action", "tree_9a5efe5d0e9b43a1", "tyia", "uncategorized_talent", "use_the_force"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "skill", "value": 1, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["attack.when-hit", "proximity.ally-nearby"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Tyia Adept"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.421Z", "detectedPredicates": ["attack.when-hit", "proximity.ally-nearby"]}}}
