{"_id": "93770927eba5446d", "name": "Opportunistic Strike", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "", "benefit": "Once per encounter, you can make an Attack of Opportunity against an opponent within Point-Blank Range (even using a ranged weapon), if that opponent provokes an Attack of Opportunity from one of your allies.", "description": {"value": "Once per encounter, you can make an Attack of Opportunity against an opponent within Point-Blank Range (even using a ranged weapon), if that opponent provokes an Attack of Opportunity from one of your allies."}, "class": "21dfe84d159a1b7f", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Scoundrel", "treeId": "6367600ed3c0cfae", "tags": ["action-economy", "battlefield-control", "controller", "mobility", "positioning", "ranged", "scoundrel"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 2, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["attack.with-ranged", "turn.once-per-round"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Opportunistic Strike"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.opportunistic_strike", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.422Z", "detectedPredicates": ["attack.with-ranged", "turn.once-per-round"]}}}
{"_id": "9379daa94a228c04", "name": "Block", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "", "benefit": "As a Reaction, you may negate a melee attack by making a successful Use the Force check. The DC of the check is equal to the result of the attack roll you wish to negate, and you must take a cumulative -5 penalty on your Use the Force check for every time you have used Block or Deflect since the beginning of your last turn.", "description": {"value": "As a Reaction, you may negate a melee attack by making a successful Use the Force check. The DC of the check is equal to the result of the attack roll you wish to negate, and you must take a cumulative -5 penalty on your Use the Force check for every time you have used Block or Deflect since the beginning of your last turn.\n\nYou may use the Block Talent to negate melee Area Attacks, such as those made by the Whirlwind Attack Feat. If you succeed on the Use the Force check, you take half damage if the attack hits, and no damage if the attack misses. You may spend a Force Point to use this Talent to negate an attack against an adjacent character.\n\nYou must have a Lightsaber drawn and ignited to use this Talent, and you must be aware of the attack and not Flat-Footed."}, "class": "fec1f8af44fcc35a", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Jedi", "treeId": "a67faf2ae089ab5d", "tags": ["action-economy", "armor", "dark-side", "defender", "force", "force-offense", "jedi", "lightsaber", "melee", "mobility", "ranged", "striker", "support", "sustained-damage"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 2, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["attack.with-melee"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Block"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.block", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.422Z", "detectedPredicates": ["attack.with-melee"]}}}
{"_id": "93a41831fe6bfc09", "name": "Nowhere to Run", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "Hunter's Mark, Hunter's Target, Nowhere to Hide", "benefit": "Once per turn, whenever an opponent whom you selected for your Hunter's Target attempts to Withdraw, you can make an Attack of Opportunity against that target.", "description": {"value": "Once per turn, whenever an opponent whom you selected for your Hunter's Target attempts to Withdraw, you can make an Attack of Opportunity against that target."}, "class": "336bba6d1e517c92", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Bounty Hunter", "prerequisitesStructured": {"type": "all", "conditions": [{"type": "talent", "id": "swse.talent.nowhere_to_hide"}, {"type": "talent", "id": "swse.talent.hunters_target"}], "_source": "canonical-csv"}, "treeId": "a47ed82a822e3962", "tags": ["feat-chain", "mobility", "scoundrel", "talent-chain"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 0, "type": "untyped", "predicates": [], "enabled": false, "priority": 500, "description": "[REQUIRES MANUAL MAPPING] Nowhere to Run"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.nowhere_to_run", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.422Z", "detectedPredicates": []}}}
{"_id": "9408056ede41b43f", "name": "Cast Suspicion", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "", "benefit": "As a Swift Action, you can select one enemy within your line of sight. That enemy loses all morale and insight bonuses on attack rolls and cannot be aided (using the Aid Another Action) by its allies until the end of your next turn.", "description": {"value": "As a Swift Action, you can select one enemy within your line of sight. That enemy loses all morale and insight bonuses on attack rolls and cannot be aided (using the Aid Another Action) by its allies until the end of your next turn."}, "class": "8c58016e587dd2c7", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Noble", "treeId": "da34105c875650ae", "tags": ["action-economy", "defender", "leader", "melee", "noble", "positioning", "ranged", "skills", "social", "striker", "support"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "defense.reflex", "value": 2, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["defense.against-ranged", "defense.against-melee", "defense.reflex", "defense.will", "attack.when-hit", "attack.with-melee", "attack.with-ranged", "proximity.ally-nearby"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Cast Suspicion"}]}}, "effects": [{"_id": "c6a962d9-bdbf-4119-82bb-4d0344f3bf83", "name": "Cast Suspicion", "icon": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "changes": [{"key": "system.morale.suppressed", "mode": 5, "value": "true"}], "disabled": false, "duration": {}, "flags": {"swse": {"source": "talent", "talentName": "Cast Suspicion"}}}], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.cast_suspicion", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.422Z", "detectedPredicates": ["defense.against-ranged", "defense.against-melee", "defense.reflex", "defense.will", "attack.when-hit", "attack.with-melee", "attack.with-ranged", "proximity.ally-nearby"]}}}
{"_id": "941c1dfd00e697da", "name": "Redirect Shot", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "Deflect, Base Attack Bonus +5", "benefit": "This Talent allows you to redirect a deflected blaster bolt along a specific trajectory, so that it damages another creature or object in its path. Once per round when you successfully Deflect a blaster bolt, you can make an immediate ranged attack against another target with which you have line of sight.", "description": {"value": "This Talent allows you to redirect a deflected blaster bolt along a specific trajectory, so that it damages another creature or object in its path. Once per round when you successfully Deflect a blaster bolt, you can make an immediate ranged attack against another target with which you have line of sight.\n\nApply the normal range penalties to the attack roll, not counting the distance the bolt traveled to reach you. If the attack succeeds, it deals normal weapon damage to the target. Only single blaster bolts can be redirected in this manner. Barrages from Autofire weapons and other types of projectiles can't be redirected."}, "class": "fec1f8af44fcc35a", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Jedi", "prerequisitesStructured": {"type": "all", "conditions": [{"type": "talent", "id": "swse.talent.deflect"}, {"type": "bab", "min": 5}], "_source": "canonical-csv"}, "treeId": "2bc2572e852832e4", "tags": ["jedi", "lightsaber", "melee", "positioning", "ranged", "striker"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 5, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["attack.with-ranged"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Redirect Shot"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.redirect_shot", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.422Z", "detectedPredicates": ["attack.with-ranged"]}}}
{"_id": "9461c7aa79dd07c6", "name": "Battle Meditation", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "", "benefit": "The Jedi technique known as Battle Meditation allows you and your allies to work together seamlessly and with a level of precision that can only come from The Force. As a Full-Round Action, you can spend a Force Point to give you and all allies within 6 squares of you a +1 insight bonus on attack rolls that lasts until the end of the encounter.", "description": {"value": "The Jedi technique known as Battle Meditation allows you and your allies to work together seamlessly and with a level of precision that can only come from The Force. As a Full-Round Action, you can spend a Force Point to give you and all allies within 6 squares of you a +1 insight bonus on attack rolls that lasts until the end of the encounter.\n\nThis bonus does not extend to allies outside the range of the effect, even if they move within 6 squares of you later on. Allies who benefit from the Battle Meditation must remain within 6 squares of you to retain the insight bonus, and they lose it if you are knocked unconscious or killed. This is a Mind-Affecting effect.\n\nThis affects all allied Gunners within 6 squares at Starship Scale."}, "class": "fec1f8af44fcc35a", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Jedi", "treeId": "d6b4331c0e31f7e3", "tags": ["action-economy", "force", "force-offense", "jedi", "positioning", "striker", "sustained-damage"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 0, "type": "untyped", "predicates": [], "enabled": false, "priority": 500, "description": "[REQUIRES MANUAL MAPPING] Battle Meditation"}]}}, "effects": [{"_id": "0cdcb68b-7eeb-45d0-ae5c-575d13648a00", "name": "Battle Meditation", "icon": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "changes": [{"key": "system.attacks.allies", "mode": 2, "value": "1"}], "disabled": false, "duration": {}, "flags": {"swse": {"source": "talent", "talentName": "Battle Meditation"}}}], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.battle_meditation", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.422Z", "detectedPredicates": []}}}
{"_id": "9491f34aad83dfb1", "name": "Shared Notoriety", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "Notorious", "benefit": "When your Minions invoke your name, others take note. If you have Minions, they may reroll any Persuasion checks made to intimidate others, but the result of the reroll must be accepted, even if it is worse.", "description": {"value": "When your Minions invoke your name, others take note. If you have Minions, they may reroll any Persuasion checks made to intimidate others, but the result of the reroll must be accepted, even if it is worse."}, "class": "324631ca844a88be", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Crime Lord", "prerequisitesStructured": {"type": "all", "conditions": [{"type": "talent", "id": "swse.talent.notorious"}], "_source": "canonical-csv"}, "treeId": "c1be604242cb328f", "tags": ["feat-chain", "skills", "social", "talent-chain"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 0, "type": "untyped", "predicates": [], "enabled": false, "priority": 500, "description": "[REQUIRES MANUAL MAPPING] Shared Notoriety"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.shared_notoriety", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.422Z", "detectedPredicates": []}}}
{"_id": "94aa0ef55bace440", "name": "Knowledge is Life", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "SpyNet Agent", "benefit": "As a Swift Action, you can designate a single target within line of sight and make a Knowledge (Galactic Lore) check against a DC equal to 15 + the target's CL. If the check is successful, for the remainder of the encounter you gain a +2 morale bonus to the Defense Score of your choice against that target.", "description": {"value": "As a Swift Action, you can designate a single target within line of sight and make a Knowledge (Galactic Lore) check against a DC equal to 15 + the target's CL. If the check is successful, for the remainder of the encounter you gain a +2 morale bonus to the Defense Score of your choice against that target."}, "costNumeric": null, "prerequisitesStructured": {"type": "all", "conditions": [{"type": "talent", "id": "swse.talent.spynet_agent"}], "_source": "canonical-csv"}, "treeId": "d20682671d035cef", "tags": ["action_economy", "defender", "feat_chain", "investigation", "knowledge", "resources", "social", "social_network", "striker", "swift_action", "talent_chain", "tree_d20682671d035cef", "uncategorized_talent"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 0, "type": "untyped", "predicates": [], "enabled": false, "priority": 500, "description": "[REQUIRES MANUAL MAPPING] Knowledge is Life"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.knowledge_is_life", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.422Z", "detectedPredicates": []}}}
{"_id": "94adb5de4d3a7b20", "name": "Cunning Strategist", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "Disruptive, Walk the Line", "benefit": "You can create opportunities to chip away at our opponents' defenses. You can use each of the following actions once per encounter as a Standard Action:", "description": {"value": "You can create opportunities to chip away at our opponents' defenses. You can use each of the following actions once per encounter as a Standard Action:\n\nCreate Opening: Make a single melee or ranged attack against any target within your Range. If you damage the target, the target takes a -5 penalty to their Reflex Defense until the start of your next turn.\nCrippling Attack: Make a single melee or ranged attack against any target within your Range. Until the start of your next turn, the target takes a -2 penalty to their base speed.\nVicious Attack: Make a melee or ranged attack within your Range against two opponents that are within 2 squares of each other. Make separate attack rolls at a -5 penalty against each target, but roll damage once only."}, "class": "21dfe84d159a1b7f", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Scoundrel", "prerequisitesStructured": {"type": "all", "conditions": [{"type": "talent", "id": "swse.talent.walk_the_line"}], "_source": "canonical-csv"}, "treeId": "67b59e020c1660eb", "tags": ["damage-reduction", "feat-chain", "mobility", "positioning", "scoundrel", "striker", "talent-chain"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 2, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["turn.once-per-round"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Cunning Strategist"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.cunning_strategist", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.422Z", "detectedPredicates": ["turn.once-per-round"]}}}
{"_id": "94b1951d4795f602", "name": "Resilience Implant", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "", "benefit": "Once per encounter as a Standard Action, you can give one adjacent living creature a Resilience Implant. The target must be willing to receive this Implant, which grants the target a +5 Equipment bonus to it's Damage Threshold until the end of the encounter.", "description": {"value": "Once per encounter as a Standard Action, you can give one adjacent living creature a Resilience Implant. The target must be willing to receive this Implant, which grants the target a +5 Equipment bonus to it's Damage Threshold until the end of the encounter."}, "class": "557e1a5ec72166fd", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Shaper", "treeId": "d8a71a6c5b2b7581", "tags": ["ability_enhancement", "action_economy", "biotech", "category_shaper", "crafting", "defender", "gear", "healing", "implant", "leader", "new_action", "positioning", "standard_action", "striker", "support", "tree_d8a71a6c5b2b7581"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 5, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["turn.once-per-round"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Resilience Implant"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.resilience_implant", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.422Z", "detectedPredicates": ["turn.once-per-round"]}}}
{"_id": "95697c5a4459d7e4", "name": "Outmaneuver", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "Deployment Tactics, Field Tactics", "benefit": "An Officer learns to counter the tactics of their enemies. As a Standard Action, you can make a DC 15 Knowledge (Tactics) check. If the check succeeds, opponents in your line of sight lose all competence, insight, and morale bonuses on attack rolls, as well as any dodge bonuses to Reflex Defense, until the start of your next turn.", "description": {"value": "An Officer learns to counter the tactics of their enemies. As a Standard Action, you can make a DC 15 Knowledge (Tactics) check. If the check succeeds, opponents in your line of sight lose all competence, insight, and morale bonuses on attack rolls, as well as any dodge bonuses to Reflex Defense, until the start of your next turn.\n\nIf one or more enemy Officers are within your line of sight, the highest level Officer among them can attempt to Oppose your Knowledge (Tactics) check as a Reaction. If their Skill Check result is higher than yours, your attempt to Outmaneuver your opponents fails."}, "class": "30b9cd24b80ebf46", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Officer", "prerequisitesStructured": {"type": "all", "conditions": [{"type": "talent", "id": "swse.talent.field_tactics"}], "_source": "canonical-csv"}, "treeId": "9253ace716c3e966", "tags": ["defender", "evasion", "feat-chain", "leader", "scout", "skills", "talent-chain"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "defense.reflex", "value": 2, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["defense.reflex"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Outmaneuver"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.outmaneuver", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.422Z", "detectedPredicates": ["defense.reflex"]}}}
{"_id": "95ae8969ac50b180", "name": "Make Do", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": null, "benefit": "No penalty when using improvised weapons.", "description": "You take no penalty when using improvised weapons.", "class": "f62ca2e639cab614", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Soldier", "treeId": "67fdd8dce9abd6c1", "tags": ["soldier"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 0, "type": "untyped", "predicates": [], "enabled": false, "priority": 500, "description": "[REQUIRES MANUAL MAPPING] Make Do"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.make_do", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.422Z", "detectedPredicates": []}}}
{"_id": "962c8a24f9caaba0", "name": "Rally", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "Born Leader, Distant Command", "benefit": "Once per encounter, you can rally your allies and bring them back from the edge of defeat. As a Swift Action, any allies within your line of sight who have less than half their total hit points remaining gain a +2 morale bonus to their Reflex Defense and Will Defense, and a +2 bonus to all damage rolls for the remainder of the encounter.", "description": {"value": "Once per encounter, you can rally your allies and bring them back from the edge of defeat. As a Swift Action, any allies within your line of sight who have less than half their total hit points remaining gain a +2 morale bonus to their Reflex Defense and Will Defense, and a +2 bonus to all damage rolls for the remainder of the encounter.\n\nUnlike other Mind-Affecting Talents, Rally affects both allied Vehicles and characters with less than half their Hit Points. The Vehicle gains a +2 bonus to its Reflex Defense, all crewmembers gain a +2 bonus to their Will Defense so long as they are on board, and all Gunners gain a +2 bonus on damage with Weapon Systems (before multiplier, if any). Any crewmember who has less than half its Hit Points also gains the normal benefits of this Talent even if it leaves the Vehicle, but note that these bonuses do not stack."}, "class": "8c58016e587dd2c7", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Noble", "prerequisitesStructured": {"type": "all", "conditions": [{"type": "talent", "id": "swse.talent.distant_command"}], "_source": "canonical-csv"}, "treeId": "5964237d22681dc0", "tags": ["defender", "noble", "scaling", "striker"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "defense.reflex", "value": 2, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["defense.reflex", "defense.will", "attack.when-hit"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Rally"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.rally", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.422Z", "detectedPredicates": ["defense.reflex", "defense.will", "attack.when-hit"]}}}
