{"_id": "b62303265cab4eeb", "name": "Galactic Guidance", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "Trained in Knowledge (Galactic Lore)", "description": {"value": "You share your considerable galactic knowledge to inform others' actions and decisions. Once per encounter, as a Reaction, if you succeed on a DC 25 Knowledge (Galactic Lore) check, you enable one ally within 6 squares of you to reroll a failed Intelligence or Wisdom based Skill Check (other than Perception)."}, "benefit": "You share your considerable galactic knowledge to inform others' actions and decisions. Once per encounter, as a Reaction, if you succeed on a DC 25 Knowledge (Galactic Lore) check, you enable one ally within 6 squares of you to reroll a failed Intelligence or Wisdom based Skill Check (other than Perception).", "class": "", "category": "", "costNumeric": null, "treeId": "0b5857edbcf049a2", "tags": ["action_economy", "controller", "defender", "feat_chain", "guidance", "investigation", "knowledge", "leader", "mobility", "perception", "positioning", "reaction", "skills", "social", "striker", "support", "talent_chain", "tree_0b5857edbcf049a2", "uncategorized_talent"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "defense.will", "value": 5, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["defense.will", "attack.when-hit", "proximity.ally-nearby", "turn.once-per-round"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Galactic Guidance"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.425Z", "detectedPredicates": ["defense.will", "attack.when-hit", "proximity.ally-nearby", "turn.once-per-round"]}}}
{"_id": "b6287de11cbb4bef", "name": "Tactical Edge", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "", "benefit": "You can use the Assault Tactics, Deployment Tactics, or Field Tactics Talent as a Swift Action, instead of a Move Action (provided you have the Talent in question).", "description": {"value": "You can use the Assault Tactics, Deployment Tactics, or Field Tactics Talent as a Swift Action, instead of a Move Action (provided you have the Talent in question)."}, "class": "30b9cd24b80ebf46", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Officer", "treeId": "9253ace716c3e966", "tags": ["action-economy", "mobility"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 0, "type": "untyped", "predicates": [], "enabled": false, "priority": 500, "description": "[REQUIRES MANUAL MAPPING] Tactical Edge"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.tactical_edge", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.425Z", "detectedPredicates": []}}}
{"_id": "b66c142c79341858", "name": "Veiled Biotech", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "Trained in Stealth", "benefit": "You gain a +10 competence bonus on Deception and Stealth checks made to conceal any Biotechnology or any Bio-Implants you possess. Additionally, you may draw a concealed Biotech item or Weapon as a Swift Action instead of a Standard Action; if you then make an attack with the Biotech Weapon before the end of your turn, your opponent loses it's Dexterity bonus to it's Reflex Defense against the first attack you make with that Weapon.", "description": {"value": "You gain a +10 competence bonus on Deception and Stealth checks made to conceal any Biotechnology or any Bio-Implants you possess. Additionally, you may draw a concealed Biotech item or Weapon as a Swift Action instead of a Standard Action; if you then make an attack with the Biotech Weapon before the end of your turn, your opponent loses it's Dexterity bonus to it's Reflex Defense against the first attack you make with that Weapon."}, "class": "21dfe84d159a1b7f", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Scoundrel", "prerequisitesStructured": {"type": "all", "conditions": [{"type": "skillTrained", "skill": "6d2ac22d9fcf402f"}], "_source": "canonical-csv"}, "treeId": "33c3210fcac8c664", "tags": ["action-economy", "defender", "feat-chain", "mobility", "scoundrel", "skills", "social", "stealth", "striker", "talent-chain"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 0, "type": "untyped", "predicates": [], "enabled": false, "priority": 500, "description": "[REQUIRES MANUAL MAPPING] Veiled Biotech"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.veiled_biotech", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.425Z", "detectedPredicates": []}}}
{"_id": "b6e600188cf5597f", "name": "Bayonet Master", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "Gun Club", "benefit": "When you take a Full Attack Action, you can treat a ranged weapon with a Bayonet (or Vibrobayonet) as a Double Weapon. You can attack with the Bayonet (or Vibrobayonet) and club a target with your ranged Weapon (as with the Gun Club Talent), ignoring the normal penalties for attacking with both ends of a Double Weapon.", "description": {"value": "When you take a Full Attack Action, you can treat a ranged weapon with a Bayonet (or Vibrobayonet) as a Double Weapon. You can attack with the Bayonet (or Vibrobayonet) and club a target with your ranged Weapon (as with the Gun Club Talent), ignoring the normal penalties for attacking with both ends of a Double Weapon."}, "class": "f62ca2e639cab614", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Soldier", "prerequisitesStructured": {"type": "all", "conditions": [{"type": "talent", "id": "swse.talent.gun_club"}], "_source": "canonical-csv"}, "treeId": "67fdd8dce9abd6c1", "tags": ["feat-chain", "positioning", "ranged", "soldier", "talent-chain"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 2, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["attack.with-ranged"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Bayonet Master"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.bayonet_master", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.425Z", "detectedPredicates": ["attack.with-ranged"]}}}
{"_id": "b6e75c52f5d66ade", "name": "Wild Sense", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "Charm Beast", "benefit": "As a Swift Action once per turn, you can make a Use the Force check to touch the mind of a Beast with an Indifferent or better Attitude toward you, provided it is within 12 squares of you and in your line of sight. When you do so, the Beast makes an immediate active Perception check, and you are considered to perceive everything the Beast does, including noticing targets, as though you had made the check.", "description": {"value": "As a Swift Action once per turn, you can make a Use the Force check to touch the mind of a Beast with an Indifferent or better Attitude toward you, provided it is within 12 squares of you and in your line of sight. When you do so, the Beast makes an immediate active Perception check, and you are considered to perceive everything the Beast does, including noticing targets, as though you had made the check."}, "class": "289fcf920ef0e184", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Force Adept", "prerequisitesStructured": {"type": "all", "conditions": [{"type": "talent", "id": "swse.talent.charm_beast"}], "_source": "canonical-csv"}, "treeId": "ed899f9f41fc1391", "tags": ["action_economy", "beast_companion", "category_force_adept", "controller", "feat_chain", "force", "force_capacity", "force_execution", "force_training", "mystic", "nature", "perception", "positioning", "skills", "support", "survival", "swift_action", "talent_chain", "tree_ed899f9f41fc1391", "use_the_force"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 0, "type": "untyped", "predicates": [], "enabled": false, "priority": 500, "description": "[REQUIRES MANUAL MAPPING] Wild Sense"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.wild_sense", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.425Z", "detectedPredicates": []}}}
{"_id": "b788095a71a47be7", "name": "Riposte", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "Block, Base Attack Bonus +5", "benefit": "As a Reaction once per encounter, you can make a Lightsaber attack against a being whose attack you successfully negated using the Block Talent. Only non-area melee attacks can be Riposted in this manner; you cannot use this Talent when negating the damage from melee Area Attacks (such as those made with the Whirlwind Attack feat).", "description": {"value": "As a Reaction once per encounter, you can make a Lightsaber attack against a being whose attack you successfully negated using the Block Talent. Only non-area melee attacks can be Riposted in this manner; you cannot use this Talent when negating the damage from melee Area Attacks (such as those made with the Whirlwind Attack feat)."}, "class": "fec1f8af44fcc35a", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Jedi", "prerequisitesStructured": {"type": "all", "conditions": [{"type": "talent", "id": "swse.talent.block"}, {"type": "bab", "min": 5}], "_source": "canonical-csv"}, "treeId": "b3c5d90b5036f39b", "tags": ["force", "force-offense", "jedi"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 0, "type": "untyped", "predicates": [], "enabled": false, "priority": 500, "description": "[REQUIRES MANUAL MAPPING] Riposte"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.riposte", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.425Z", "detectedPredicates": []}}}
{"_id": "b7caecab09bb3f77", "name": "Relentless Pursuit", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "", "benefit": "You may roll twice for any opposed Pilot check made to initiate a Dogfight, keeping the better result.", "description": {"value": "You may roll twice for any opposed Pilot check made to initiate a Dogfight, keeping the better result."}, "class": "9c9989c34714f920", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Ace Pilot", "treeId": "b17c1515c06361d6", "tags": ["scout"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 0, "type": "untyped", "predicates": [], "enabled": false, "priority": 500, "description": "[REQUIRES MANUAL MAPPING] Relentless Pursuit"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.relentless_pursuit", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.425Z", "detectedPredicates": []}}}
{"_id": "b7d5a1bc3d40b964", "name": "Keep It Together", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "", "benefit": "Once per encounter, when a Vehicle you're Piloting takes damage that equals or exceeds its Damage Threshold, your Vehicle avoids moving down the Condition Track.", "description": {"value": "Once per encounter, when a Vehicle you're Piloting takes damage that equals or exceeds its Damage Threshold, your Vehicle avoids moving down the Condition Track."}, "class": "9c9989c34714f920", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Ace Pilot", "prerequisitesStructured": {"type": "all", "conditions": [{"type": "talent", "id": "swse.talent.jury_rigger"}], "_source": "canonical-csv"}, "treeId": "b17c1515c06361d6", "tags": ["condition-removal", "controller", "evasion", "scout"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "attack", "value": 2, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["turn.once-per-round"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Keep It Together"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.keep_it_together", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.425Z", "detectedPredicates": ["turn.once-per-round"]}}}
{"_id": "b812c197daea93fd", "name": "Multiattack Proficiency (pistols)", "type": "talent", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"prerequisites": "", "benefit": "Dual Weapon Mastery I, Weapon Focus (Pistols) Immediately after making a Full Attack where you attack with two Pistols, you may move up to your Speed as a Free Action. Reference Book: Star Wars Saga Edition Galaxy of Intrigue You are a master of the elegant, if archaic, custom of dueling with Pistols. You can use each of the following Actions once per encounter as a Standard Action: End Game: You make a single ranged attack with a Pistol against an opponent within Range. The opponent's Damage Threshold is halved (rounded down) for the purpose of this attack. Snap Aiming: You make a single ranged attack with the benefits of Aiming. Stand Ready: You gain a +4 bonus to your Reflex Defense until the end of your next turn and make a single ranged attack. Reference Book: Star Wars Saga Edition Scum and Villainy If you are within 6 squares of a target and are armed with a Pistol or a Rifle, you can act as though you occupied the nearest square adjacent to the target for purposes of determining whether or not you or any allies are Flanking that target. You may only be considered to be Flanking a single target at a time. You must spend a Swift Action on your turn to designate the target you Flank at range. Reference Book: Star Wars Saga Edition Unknown Regions When moving away from a pursuing target, if you either Run or use two Move Actions during this turn, you can make a single ranged attack with a -5 penalty as part of your Move Action. You can spend a Force Point to avoid the penalty. Reference Book: Star Wars Saga Edition Unknown Regions", "description": {"value": ""}, "class": "162d866ba36fce69", "costNumeric": null, "category": "Gunslinger", "treeId": "cb6f775cd227a3e3", "tags": ["action-economy", "controller", "defender", "dual-wield", "evasion", "force", "force-control", "force-defense", "force-offense", "mobility", "positioning", "ranged", "striker", "sustained-damage"], "executionModel": "PASSIVE", "subType": "STATE", "abilityMeta": {"modifiers": [{"target": "defense.reflex", "value": 4, "type": "untyped", "predicates": ["defense.against-ranged", "defense.reflex", "attack.with-ranged", "turn.on-current-turn", "turn.once-per-round"], "enabled": true, "priority": 500, "description": "Multiattack Proficiency (pistols)"}]}}, "effects": [], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0}, "flags": {"swse": {"id": "swse.talent.multiattack_proficiency_pistols", "migratedToState": true, "migrationDate": "2026-03-08T18:22:17.426Z", "detectedPredicates": ["defense.against-ranged", "defense.reflex", "attack.with-ranged", "turn.on-current-turn", "turn.once-per-round"]}}}
